messages.message:
Hopped on a call with David, we narrowed it down and it happens when you have the “Enable new navigation top bar” feature enabled.

The home page, settings page, and hub page are cut off at the bottom, not sure about other pages. @Paul H not sure what component is causing the issue though

P.S. is it intentional for the “Workspaces” and “Hub” button in the top bar to be left aligned instead of centered?
